Package org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs

Apache Beam FileSystem interfaces and their default implementations.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MoveOptions
    An object that configures FileSystems.copy(java.util.List<org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.ResourceId>, java.util.List<org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.ResourceId>, org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.MoveOptions...), FileSystems.rename(java.util.List<org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.ResourceId>, java.util.List<org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.ResourceId>, org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.MoveOptions...), and FileSystems.delete(java.util.Collection<org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.ResourceId>, org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.MoveOptions...).
    ResolveOptions
    An object that configures ResourceId.resolve(java.lang.String, org.apache.beam.sdk.io.fs.ResolveOptions).
    ResourceId
    An identifier which represents a file-like resource.
